A way to fix this is to alternate between the default logrus text formatter and a raw text formatter whenever the terminal is in raw mode. 

The raw text formatter can just append an extra ```\r``` to the default text formatter: 
```go
type RawTtyFormatter struct {
}

func (f *RawTtyFormatter) Format(entry *logrus.Entry) ([]byte, error) {
	textFormatter := logrus.TextFormatter{}
	bytes, err := textFormatter.Format(entry)

	if err == nil {
		bytes = append(bytes, '\r')
	}

	return bytes, err
}
````
